    imgUrl: '/bggenre/fullonpower.jpg',
    title: 'Full On Power',
    description:
    "Psytrance Full-on Power is an intense and energetic subgenre of psychedelic trance music that delivers a high-energy and powerful sonic experience on the dance floor. It combines the driving rhythms and basslines of psytrance with dynamic melodies, intricate sound design, and a relentless pace to create a thrilling and exhilarating musical journey.\n\nHere are some key features and characteristics of the Psytrance Full-on Power genre:\n\n- High Energy and Intensity: Psytrance Full-on Power is known for its high-energy and intense nature, with fast tempos ranging from 140 to 150 BPM or higher.\n\n- Powerful Basslines: The genre features powerful and driving basslines that dominate the mix, adding a strong foundation and visceral impact.\n\n- Dynamic Melodies and Leads: Psytrance Full-on Power incorporates intricate and fast-paced melodies and leads, creating an energetic and uplifting atmosphere.\n\n- Layered Soundscapes: The genre utilizes layered soundscapes and textures, incorporating sound effects, atmospheric elements, and psychedelic motifs.\n\n- Driving Percussion: Psytrance Full-on Power includes rhythmic and driving percussion elements, with intricate drum patterns and engaging rhythm sections.\n\n- Builds and Drops: Tracks in this genre often feature extended build-ups and explosive drops, creating tension, release, and excitement.\n\n- Psychedelic Elements: As a subgenre of psytrance, Psytrance Full-on Power incorporates psychedelic sound effects, modulations, and twisted synth patterns.\n\nNotable artists in the Psytrance Full-on Power genre include Vini Vici, Astrix, Avalon, Blastoyz, Electric Universe, and Sesto Sento, among others.\n\nOverall, Psytrance Full-on Power delivers a thrilling and powerful experience on the dance floor, combining fast tempos, driving basslines, dynamic melodies, and layered soundscapes for an immersive and exhilarating sonic journey.",
